 </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Autel de</supplied> Péan.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Altar of</supplied> Paean.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Altare di</supplied> Peana.</p>
            </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>About the clearance of the area and the discovery of the group of altars (<ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr102800</ref>,  <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr102900</ref>, 
                    <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr103000</ref>, <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr103200</ref>, <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr103300</ref>, <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr103430</ref>) 
                    see <bibl><ptr target="#luni2014b"/>, p. <citedRange>141</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
	<p/>
